        "pb_svc_2_user": "[TL] Upgrade your fixtures to high-efficiency, water-saving technologies.",
        "pb_svc_2_tech": "[TL] Installation of WaterSense certified fixtures, pressure compensating aerators, and dual-flush mechanisms to optimize volumetric flow rates and comply with local conservation mandates.",
