        "pb_svc_3_user": "[TL] Custom plumbing blueprints and system sizing for your property.",
        "pb_svc_3_tech": "[TL] Calculations based on fixture unit (FU) demand, static pressure analysis, and friction loss equations to engineer optimal pipe diameters and material selections.",
