        "pb_svc_5_user": "[VI] Comprehensive septic tank installation, repair, and biological optimization.",
        "pb_svc_5_tech": "[VI] Soil percolation analysis, leach field sizing, and installation of multi-chamber bio-reactors with effluent filters to ensure optimal anaerobic decomposition.",
